description.et: Maa-amet on Eesti riigi kompetentsikeskus maaküsimustes ning suurim ruumiandmete tootja, haldaja, levitaja ja ruumiandmeteenuste pakkuja.
description.en: The Land Board is a national competency centre in land related matters and the biggest producer, manager and distributor of spatial data as well as provider of spatial data services.
